des:
Modern Flames products help you control home appliance.You can simply ask Alexa to turn on or turn off your Modern Flames.
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust your Modern Flames - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo.
After connecting Alexa to your Modern Flames products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Modern Flames" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register an account in our "Modern Flames" app;
(3). You need to have some Modern Flames devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "Modern Flames" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Modern Flames" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Modern Flames" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Modern Flames", and you'll be navigated to "Modern Flames" login page;
(9). Open “Modern Flames“ App, click More Service, choose “Alexa”. Link with Verification Code, copy the Code, put code into the login page；
(10). Now all setup is finished.
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on Modern Flames.”
“Alexa, turn off Modern Flames.”
Note: Modern Flames is a heater.
